 "remarks": "Welcome to this beautifully maintained townhome offering a stylish and functional layout in Stamford&apos;s desirable Glenbrook neighborhood. The main level features an inviting open floor plan with comfortable living space and an updated kitchen with crisp white cabinetry, stainless steel appliances, beautiful countertops, under-cabinet lighting, and ample cabinetry. Step outside to the private deck, a great spot to enjoy your morning coffee or unwind at the end of the day. Upstairs, you&apos;ll find a spacious bedroom, full bathroom, convenient laundry closet, and plenty of closet space. Additional highlights include a one car garage beneath the building and a large private storage room. Ideally located close to the Glenbrook Metro-North station, shopping, restaurants, parks, and everyday amenities, this townhouse combines low-maintenance living with convenient access to downtown Stamford and surrounding Fairfield County. A wonderful opportunity to enjoy an updated home with an open layout, private outdoor space, garage parking, low HOA fees and a convenient Glenbrook location.",
